
```{=html}
<% for (const item of items) { %>

<h2><%- item.category %></h2>

<p><%- item.description %></p>

<div class="list grid" style="column-gap: 10px;">

<% for (const tile of item.tiles) { %>
  <div class="card border-2 rounded-1 g-col-12 g-col-sm-6 g-col-md-4 mb-2" <%= metadataAttrs(tile) %>>
    <div class="card-header py-1 px-2 border-bottom border-1 bg-light">
      <small class="card-text inline-block">
        <a href="<%- tile.path %>" class="listing-title"><%= tile.title %></a>
        <br>
        <span class="text-muted listing-subtitle"><%= tile.subtitle %></span>
      </small>
    </div>
    <div class="listing-image">
      <a href="<%- tile.path %>">
        <img src="<%- tile.image %>" alt="<%- tile.description %>" class="card-img-top"/>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
<% } %>

</div>

<% } %>
```
